  explanation: 'This is the main mission manager, and it contains a list of all the
    station systems in each level. These station systems can be used as a physical
    mission board or just an invisible element to configure different missions which
    are maybe activate by dialog or trigger.


    Each station has a list of missions,
    which are the one which contains the missions to achieve, task, rewards and events
    to activate.'
